text:
Guddu Bhaiya zindabaad.
Sabse chill banda apni wing ka, tension lete waqt bhi hasta hi rehta hai. Tere saath milkar Sagnik ko kitta daraya hai. Tere ghar pr jo party me naache the yaar. 
Sabse scheduled aur helpful ladka apne wing ki.

Bhai milte rhenge baar baar, aage bhi.
author: Sudhanshu  Mishra

text:
Best guy to hangout with. Confidence hamesha full. 
Tere aur Saksham ke videos hai mere pass, batan jab wo sunehre lamhe firse dekhne honge tumhe.
Bakchod baddy player.
author: Sudhanshu  Mishra

text:
Can't say that I have spent more time with any other guy at IITK. Started by being Bros through IITK culture, to becoming bros for life. As far as I have known him, iske ghar pr allowed nhi mai , mostly his fault for telling his mom about dynamite and Altaaf bhai. But despite that, we have remained friends for long. From being unusual roommates in 2nd year to destroying everyone at R6 2v5. Ye nightout nahi maarta tha 1st year me, to playing FIFA all night after that. Only place where i'll say, " Pro gamer to tu hai except FIFA obviously". Despite so much bakchodi during our stay, I know gazab chaapu banda hai ye. I cherish all the philosophical discussions that we had while going to sleep. I surely can't imagine IITK without you. Best Luck bro.  
PS : Ye whi launda hai who prefers to stay in his room than go on a Trek. Japan me room chodke ghoomne chalenge. 
PPS : He has something that I. Kishan and Saksham agree is the best in our wing :P
author: Sudhanshu  Mishra

text: Gazab chaapu banda hai bhai. Usse bhi zyada mazedaar hai iski baatein sunna. Master of managing everything. Bada aadmi banke T-Bhai ko mat bhool jaana.
author: Sudhanshu  Mishra

text:
Bhai Bhai bhai, kya hi kahoo tere baare me. 
Tum aur Nikhil alag hi level pr ho. A fellow movie and anime maniac. 

3rd year ka trip jab plan kiya tha tumne hi kataya tha sabse pehle but it was destined to fail. Abhi next trip karna hai saath me kuch bhi karke. 5th semester se permanent resident ban gye the tumbhi humare room ke. 

All the best yaar.
Japan ka batata hoo, although koshish poori hai.
author: Sudhanshu  Mishra

text:
Kaafi bakchodiyan ki bhai tere saath. 
Most weird memory of college life was acting like your girlfriend to scare your stalker.
Milte hai bhai firse kaafi kahaniyan sunni hai.
author: Sudhanshu  Mishra

text:
My fellow Sudhanshu. 
Mech nhi nikalti tere bina. Kuch bhi doubt ho tere pass hi aata tha mai.
Total chill banda.
Abhi to ek saal aur nikalna hai saath me. Hope to meet you soon and make more memories.
author: Sudhanshu  Mishra
